Additions:
Support for in-app updates
Anonymous usage stat reporting. This is disabled by default, please opt in if you're interested in helping Wearable Extensions grow
More tests.

Changes & Fixes:
Reworked how the selected watch status is shown and updated
Reworked setting up watches
Updated the app's styles to be more consistent
You should see stability and consistency improvements for the foreseeable future

Removals:
Built-in changelog, you can see what's new via the in-app link to GitHub